  <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n                \n\n<div class=\"kksr-legend\" style=\"font-size: 19.2px;\">\n            4.6\/5 - (32 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>GIA S\u01af CHUY\u00caN V\u0102N \u2013 CHUY\u00caN S\u01af PH\u1ea0M \u2013 D\u1ea0Y T\u01af DUY H\u1eccC M\u00d4N V\u0102N HI\u1ec6U QU\u1ea2<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333399; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333399; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC SINH KH\u00d4NG HI\u1ec2U B\u00c0I<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333399; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>Hotline: 0962.005.996 \u2013 0987.005.996<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #282828;\"><strong>GIA S\u01af TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T &#8211; CUNG C\u1ea4P GIA S\u01af T\u1ea4T C\u1ea2 C\u00c1C M\u00d4N<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">\n<div aria-label=\"Các dịch vụ gia sư\" class=\"tri-viet-service-grid\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:16px;margin:24px 0;\"><section style=\"border:1px solid #d8eadf;border-top:4px solid #096f47;border-radius:10px;padding:20px;background:#f6fbf8;\"><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 10px;color:#096f47;font-size:20px;\">Gia sư các môn văn hóa</h3><p style=\"margin:0;color:#282828;\">Dạy Toán, Lý, Hóa, Tiếng Anh, Ngữ Văn, Lịch Sử và các môn Tiểu học từ lớp 1 đến lớp 12.</p></section><section style=\"border:1px solid #d8eadf;border-top:4px solid #096f47;border-radius:10px;padding:20px;background:#f6fbf8;\"><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 10px;color:#096f47;font-size:20px;\">Gia sư ngoại ngữ</h3><p style=\"margin:0;color:#282828;\">Dạy Tiếng Anh, Tiếng Hàn, Tiếng Trung, Tiếng Nhật và luyện giao tiếp theo nhu cầu.</p></section><section style=\"border:1px solid #d8eadf;border-top:4px solid #096f47;border-radius:10px;padding:20px;background:#f6fbf8;\"><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 10px;color:#096f47;font-size:20px;\">Ôn thi và học nâng cao</h3><p style=\"margin:0;color:#282828;\">Luyện thi chuyển cấp, thi THPT, thi học sinh giỏi và củng cố kiến thức từ cơ bản đến nâng cao.</p></section></div><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"I_%E2%80%93_BIEU_HIEN_CON_CAN_GIA_SU_VAN\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">I &#8211; BI\u1ec2U HI\u1ec6N CON C\u1ea6N GIA S\u01af V\u0102N<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Con b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t m\u00f4n V\u0103n kh\u00f4ng? Con c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u0103n, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n 8\/10 h\u1ecdc sinh ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc thu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng, thu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng&#8230;&#8230; \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m con s\u1ee3?<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0C\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh v\u0103n c\u1ee7a con k\u00e9m, ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n h\u1eb9p?<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Con kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea1o c\u00e1ch tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i v\u0103n ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh. Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1edf b\u00e0i, th\u00e2n b\u00e0i, k\u1ebft b\u00e0i?<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Con ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o v\u0103n m\u1eabu, l\u00e2u d\u1ea7n s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh th\u00f3i quen x\u1ea5u.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Con kh\u00f4ng theo k\u1ecbp b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 tr\u00ean l\u1edbp?<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Con c\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng cao ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c trong c\u00e1c k\u00ec thi quan tr\u1ecdng: H\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, th\u00ec h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3, thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p&#8230;.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3911 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/GIA-SU-Van-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/GIA-SU-Van-1.png 1000w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/GIA-SU-Van-1-300x180.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/GIA-SU-Van-1-768x461.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\">==&gt; N\u1ebfu con \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean, gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1ebft l\u00e0 cha m\u1eb9 n\u00ean t\u00ecm cho con m\u1ed9t <strong>gia s\u01b0 v\u0103n<\/strong> d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0. Gia s\u01b0 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap con th\u00e1o g\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn con c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc thu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1edb, t\u0103ng v\u1ed1n t\u1eeb&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"II_%E2%80%93_TRUNG_TAM_GIA_SU_VAN_DAY_TAI_NHA_UY_TIN\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">II &#8211; TRUNG T\u00c2M GIA S\u01af V\u0102N D\u1ea0Y T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0 UY T\u00cdN<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 uy t\u00edn, l\u00e0 n\u01a1i g\u1eedi g\u1eafm ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u cha m\u1eb9 hi\u1ec7n nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0 12 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u, tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p <strong>gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n v\u0103n<\/strong> gi\u1ecfi, c\u00f3 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0 H\u01a1n 500+ gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y v\u0103n gi\u1ecfi v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc kh\u1ed1i C t\u1eeb 9+ \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1edf l\u00ean, c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c <strong>gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n v\u0103n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0 Gia s\u01b0 v\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng TOP 1 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0: S\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m, \u0110H Qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0110H KHXH &amp; NV, \u0110H Lu\u1eadt&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0 C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 \u0111ang d\u1ea1y m\u00f4n V\u0103n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea5p 1,2,3 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. C\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 c\u00f3 kinh ngi\u1ec7m l\u00e2u n\u0103m trong ngh\u1ec1, gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y cho nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc sinh nh\u01b0: m\u1ea5t g\u1ed1c, ngh\u1ecbch, trung b\u00ecnh, luy\u1ec7n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, luy\u1ec7n thi chuy\u00ean, chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea5p, \u00f4n thi \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0 Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 1 trong nh\u1eefng trung t\u00e2m uy t\u00edn s\u1ed1 1 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, sinh vi\u00ean theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"III_%E2%80%93_HOC_PHI_GIA_SU_MON_VAN_THAM_KHAO\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 115%;\"><strong>III &#8211; H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af M\u00d4N V\u0102N THAM KH\u1ea2O<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3852 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Gia-su-VAN.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Gia-su-VAN.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Gia-su-VAN-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Gia-su-VAN-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i, h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tu\u1ef3 theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 hotline:\u00a0<span style=\"\">0962.005.996<\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #0000ff;\">Xem th\u00eam:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\">[B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1] <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-bang-gia-gia-su-tai-nha-hn-mon-toan-anh-van-hoa-ly\/\"><strong>H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0<\/strong><\/a><\/span> t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i &#8211; M\u00f4n To\u00e1n, Anh, V\u0103n, Ho\u00e1, L\u00fd<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\">TOP 3000+ <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-3000-gia-su-tieng-anh-tai-nha-tang-hieu-qua-gap-5-lan\/\">gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfng anh<\/a><\/strong><\/span> t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u2013 T\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 g\u1ea5p 5 l\u1ea7n<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E2%9C%85_Chinh_sach_hoc_thu\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #008080; font-size: 115%;\"><b>\u2705 Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc th\u1eed:<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/strong>\u00a0s\u1ebd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u: Trong \u0111\u00f3 gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai bu\u1ed5i, v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc sinh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ee5 huynh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y, gi\u00e1o \u00e1n, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3812 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm.png\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm-300x201.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm-768x515.png 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"603\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\">\ud83d\udc49\u00a0Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y th\u1eed s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5 huynh, h\u1ecdc sinh y\u00ean t\u00e2m h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t c\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi con m\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\"><em>\u201d Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t, chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 sau1-2 bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f3 con \u00a0ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t ngay. V\u00ec \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u201d Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y hai m\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh m\u1ea5t ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, l\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc\u2026 \u201c<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IV_%E2%80%93_TU_VAN_LUA_CHON_GIA_SU\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>IV &#8211; T\u01af V\u1ea4N L\u1ef0A CH\u1eccN GIA S\u01af<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em>N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn sinh vi\u00ean khi:<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0N\u0103ng l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp con c\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng l\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0Con kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch h\u1ecdc v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i v\u00ec c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0Con \u0111ang h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c l\u1edbp kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u1ea5p quan tr\u1ecdng<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3622 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/cms\/2026\/07\/banner-trung-tam-gia-su-tri-viet.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/cms\/2026\/07\/banner-trung-tam-gia-su-tri-viet.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/cms\/2026\/07\/banner-trung-tam-gia-su-tri-viet.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/cms\/2026\/07\/banner-trung-tam-gia-su-tri-viet.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em>N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean khi:<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u2666 Con m\u1ea5t ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u0103n b\u1ea3n tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng. \u0110i\u1ec3m thi c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u2666 Con l\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebfng, ham ch\u01a1i, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u2666 \u0110\u00e3 h\u1ecdc v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u gia s\u01b0 sinh vi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u2666 Con b\u1ea1n \u0111ang h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c l\u1edbp cu\u1ed1i c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 5, 9, 12<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u2666 Con b\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 thi l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi c\u1ea5p tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u1ea5p huy\u1ec7n, t\u1ec9nh.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"V_%E2%80%93_CAM_KET_CUA_TRUNG_TAM_GIA_SU_TRI_VIET\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 115%;\"><strong>V &#8211; CAM K\u1ebeT C\u1ee6A TRUNG T\u00c2M GIA S\u01af TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\">Cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0<strong> MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd &#8211; \u0110\u00daNG &amp; CHU\u1ea8N<\/strong>\u00a0theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\">H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 th\u00f4ng tin r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ee9ng minh th\u01b0 &amp; th\u1ebb sinh vi\u00ean, gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean trong bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ea1y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\">T\u00ecm v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u00a0<strong>MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd<\/strong>.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>Gia s\u01b0 <strong>NGHI\u00caM T\u00daC<\/strong> trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>T\u1eadn t\u00e2m, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u1ea1y h\u1ebft b\u00e0i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft gi\u1edd.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>D\u1ea1y \u0111\u00fang ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda h\u1ecdc sinh &amp; gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 24\/7 tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong>\ud83d\udc49\u00a0<\/strong>V\u1edbi 12 n\u0103m trong d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0, s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u01a1n 15.000+ gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi, trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t cam k\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 115%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong>\ud83d\udc49\u00a0<\/strong>G\u1ecdi ngay Hotline: <strong><span style=\"\">0962.005.996<\/span> <\/strong>ho\u1eb7c<strong> <span style=\"\">0987.005.996<\/span><\/strong>\u00a0ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n 24\/7 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CONG_TY_TNHH_TRI_VIET_VIET_NAM_%E2%80%93_TRUNG_TAM_TRI_VIET\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: 115%;\"><strong>TRUNG T\u00c2M GIA S\u01af TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\"><em>\u00a0V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng 1: 40 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u00fd Ki\u00ean, C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\"><em>\u00a0V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng 2: 125 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh, Nam T\u1eeb Li\u00eam, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\"><em>\u00a0V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng 3: S\u1ed1 263 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh, ph\u01b0\u1eddng Xu\u00e2n H\u00f2a, t\u1ec9nh Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd, Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/em><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\"><em>\u260e\ufe0f Hotline: <strong><span style=\"\">0962.005.996<\/span> <\/strong>ho\u1eb7c<strong> <span style=\"\">0987.005.996<\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 115%;\"><em>Website: https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p2\">\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GIA S\u01af CHUY\u00caN V\u0102N \u2013 CHUY\u00caN S\u01af PH\u1ea0M \u2013 D\u1ea0Y T\u01af DUY H\u1eccC M\u00d4N V\u0102N HI\u1ec6U QU\u1ea2 D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3494,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"temp